            "creation_date": 1381175180,
            "body": "<p>No, <code>switch<\/code> statements do not support ranges.<\/p>\n\n<p>Think about it from the opposite end, consider storing your available discounts in an <code>enum<\/code> and have an <code>abstract<\/code> <code>applyDiscount<\/code> method that checks if each discount is applicable and applies it to the amount.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 19233314,
            "question_id": 19233234
        }
